\par\par \b \uc2 Editorial: KPK's acid test\b0\par\par\uc2 605 \uc2 words\par \uc2 23 November 2010\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 6\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2010 The Jakarta Post   \par \par \uc2 The Jakarta Post,\par \par \uc2 There seems to be a common suspicion among the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  at large that attempts are underway to keep alleged \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  mafia practices involving former \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  official Gayus Tambunan under the carpet, despite his recent sojourn to Bali, where he is believed to have met with prominent figures.\par \par \uc2 For "safety reasons", Gayus remains reluctant to disclose the real motive behind his trip or reveal the persons he allegedly met with. However, the case looks set to spark a new rift between Indonesia's two largest political powers after President Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono's Democratic Party openly threw its weight behind an investigation into alleged \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  evasion amounting to Rp 2.1 trillion (US$235 million) implicating three coal units controlled by the family of Golkar Party chairman Aburizal Bakrie.\par \par \uc2 Gayus testified at least twice in court that he received $3 million in bribes from the coal producers to help them solve their \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  problems. To the dismay of many, the police have not taken any real actions in response to his testimony.\par \par \uc2 Aburizal has repeatedly brushed aside speculation of his involvement in Gayus' vacation to Bali, although he admitted that he too, like Gayus, visited the island to watch the same international tennis tournament Gayus attended, albeit on a different day.\par \par \uc2 That Aburizal has suspected political maneuvering to undermine Golkar is behind the latest Gayus controversy casts the specter of another lengthy, energy-sapping standoff facing the country, similar to the \uc2 Bank Century\uc2  brouhaha earlier this year, unless a legal process is initiated to settle the issue beyond doubt. After all, legal \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  is what the private sector fears most in this country.\par \par \uc2 At a time when \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  trust in the police and Attorney General's Office is at its lowest, the Corruption Eradication Commission (KPK) needs to seize the initiative by replacing the police in leading the investigation into alleged \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  mafia practices and the mega \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  evasion case involving Bakrie companies and other firms.\par \par \uc2 The law on the KPK allows the anti-graft body to take over a case from other law enforcement agencies if it involves other corruption cases and many masterminds, which according to Indonesia Corruption Watch fits the Gayus bribery saga like a glove.\par \par \uc2 The KPK is deemed Indonesia's most independent law enforcement agency, and has so far proved capable of distancing itself from political intrigue. The commission had gone through a series of acid tests when it brought to justice top government officials, politicians, not to mention former \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  deputy governor Aulia Pohan, who is part of Yudhoyono's inner circle.\par \par \uc2 The credentials are a testament to the KPK's commitment to eradicating corruption, as is its capability to continue working despite its protracted institutional challenges following the legal case launched against two of its deputies, Bibit Samad Rianto and Chandra M. Hamzah. The KPK has also demonstrated to the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  that the tug of war plaguing the selection of a replacement for its former chairman Antasari Azhar has hardly affected its performance.\par \par \uc2 It indeed will be a Herculean task to deal with a delicate \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  evasion case allegedly related to a powerful figure like Aburizal Bakrie, not to mention the political repercussions that may arise and distract the country's efforts to boost \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth and improve the people's welfare.\par \par \uc2 The chance is there for the KPK, with or without any \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  request, to dig deep into the Pandora's box of the so-called \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  mafia network that many believe is both directly and indirectly responsible for impoverishment and poor infrastructure in many parts of the country.\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020101123e6bn0003i\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
