an materials and in its own way will boost the overall \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 For me the future success of the project depends upon:\par \par \uc2 Ripping out the ostentatious luxury (see above) and perhaps knocking off a couple of floors; the opposition will lessen if there is this strong signal that members are actually listening to the concerns of the people rather than feathering their own nest as usual.\par \par \uc2 Making sure that corruption is vigorously resisted and hunted down and making sure that 10 percent does not go to all the usual suspects; this can only come through transparency -- and the KPK should be formally given responsibility to police the whole thing -- vigorously. Strong cost controls should be exercised over the total project. Scotland's lamentable experience with its own parliamentary building must not be repeated here.\par \par \uc2 Following step one, the President should declare his full support for the project and declaring an end to \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 Keith Miller\par \par \uc2 Jakarta\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020110416e74g0000u\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
